                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420131-735-offence-1 t18420131-cd-122"></join>6th of January</rs>, 1 purse, value 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 crown, and 6 shillings; the property of <persName id="t18420131-name-808" type="victimName">
